@startuml SignalCaptureAI_V0_EndToEnd_Sequence
title SignalCaptureAI V0 - End-to-End Flow (Onboarding to Lead Capture)
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam BoxPadding 10

legend top right
  **Risk Levels (Transactions & Actor Swimlanes)**
  |<#White> Black Arrow | Internal / Low Risk Operation |
  |<#F2F9FF> Light Blue Box | Trusted Internal System Boundary |
  |<#Orange> Orange Arrow | PII Processing / Auth (Medium Risk) |
  |<#FFE6CC> Light Orange Box| Edge Transit / 3rd Party (Medium Risk) |
  |<#Red> Red Arrow | External PII Ingress-Egress (High Risk) |
  |<#FFCCCC> Light Red Box| Untrusted External Actors (High Risk) |
endlegend

box "Internal Operations" #E6F2FF
actor "Sales / CRM" as CRM
actor "Finance" as Finance
end box

box "Trusted Cloud Hub — EU Only (Azure Container Apps)" #F2F9FF
participant "Provisioning\nPipeline" as Pipeline
participant "Terraform (IaC)\n(OIDC Auth)" as TF
participant "Azure Infrastructure\n(EU Region)" as Azure
participant "Azure Key Vault\n(TDE + Envelope Enc)" as KV
participant "API Gateway\n(Fastify)" as Docker
participant "CosmosDB PostgreSQL\n(Citus, RLS + TDE)" as DB
participant "AI Engine\n(Claude Haiku 3.5)" as AI
participant "Whisper Service\n(OpenAI)" as Whisper
participant "Email Service\n(Graph API + ACS)" as Email
participant "Audit Service\n(Append-Only)" as Audit
end box

box "Auth (SSO)" #FFE6CC
participant "WorkOS" as IDP
end box

box "External Actors (High Risk)" #FFCCCC
actor "Client Tenant Admin" as Admin
actor "Sales Rep (Event)" as Rep
actor "Lead" as Lead
end box

== 1. Sales & Financial Approval ==
CRM -> Finance: Sale Completed (Request Order Approval)
activate Finance
Finance -> Pipeline: Approves Order & Triggers Provisioning
deactivate Finance

== 2. Async 5-Step Provisioning Pipeline (EU) ==
activate Pipeline
Pipeline -> TF: Step 1: Execute Terraform Plan/Apply (OIDC Auth)
activate TF
TF -> Azure: Provision Citus PostgreSQL\n(RLS + tenant_id sharding)
TF -> KV: Create/Assign TDE Key + Envelope Encryption Key
Azure --> TF: DB Provisioned & Encrypted (TLS 1.3 + TDE)
TF --> Pipeline: Infrastructure Ready
deactivate TF

Pipeline -[#orange]-> IDP: Step 2: Create WorkOS Organisation
IDP --[#orange]-> Pipeline: Organisation configured

Pipeline -[#orange]-> Email: Step 3: Send Magic Link Invitation\n(via invitation-engine + ACS)
Email --[#orange]-> Admin: Magic Link Email Delivered

Pipeline -> Audit: Step 4: Record Provisioning Audit Receipt
Pipeline -> Email: Step 5: Send Welcome Email (ACS)
Email --> Admin: Welcome Email Delivered

Pipeline -> CRM: Client Created & All 5 Steps Complete
deactivate Pipeline

== 3. Client Tenant Event Setup ==
Admin -[#orange]-> IDP: Login via WorkOS (SSO)
IDP --[#orange]-> Admin: Session Cookie (httpOnly, Secure, SameSite=Lax)
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: Upload Product Documentation (Firm Context)
Docker -> DB: Store Docs in Tenant DB\n(SET LOCAL tenant_id, RLS enforced)
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: Create New Tracking Event
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: Connect Microsoft 365 Mailbox (OAuth)
Docker -[#orange]-> Email: Store Encrypted OAuth Token\n(Key Vault Envelope Encryption)

== 4. Lead Capture Workflow (EU Processing) ==
Rep -[#orange]-> IDP: Login via WorkOS (SSO)
IDP --[#orange]-> Rep: Session Cookie
Rep -> Docker: Select Event
note right
  App passes signed location header
  (HMAC-SHA256) to indicate EU context.
  No external geo-routing in V0.
end note
Rep -[#red]-> Rep: Scan Business Card (Tesseract.js OCR)\n& Record Voice Note (WebM/Opus)
note right
  OCR runs client-side only.
  No business card image PII
  egress to server for OCR.
end note
Rep -[#red]-> Docker: Submit Lead Data (OCR Text + Audio)\nvia HTTPS / TLS 1.3

activate Docker
Docker -[#orange]-> Whisper: Pass Audio for Transcription
activate Whisper
note right #FFCCCC
  Voice PII transmitted to
  OpenAI external API.
  GDPR risk — DPA required.
end note
Whisper --[#orange]-> Docker: Voice Transcript (PII stripped)
deactivate Whisper
Docker -> DB: Fetch Firm Context for Cross-Reference
DB --> Docker: Firm Context Docs
Docker -[#orange]-> AI: Analyse Transcript + OCR vs Firm Context\n(XML-delimited prompt, Zod validation)
activate AI
AI --[#orange]-> Docker: Generated Draft Email (subject, HTML, text)
deactivate AI
Docker -[#orange]-> DB: Store Lead PII & Draft\n(Citus sharded by tenant_id, RLS enforced)
Docker -> Audit: Log Lead Capture Event
Docker --[#orange]-> Rep: Present Draft Email for Review
deactivate Docker

== 5. Human-in-the-Loop & Delivery ==
Rep -[#orange]-> Docker: Review & Approve Draft
Docker -> Audit: Log Draft Approval (user_id, draft hash)
Docker -[#red]-> Email: Dispatch via Microsoft 365 Graph API\n(from user's own mailbox, Mail.Send scope)
Email -[#red]-> Lead: Email Delivered (tracking pixel injected)

== 6. Tracking & Compliance ==
Email -> DB: Record Open Event (tracking pixel loaded)
Email -> DB: Record Reply Event (Graph API inbox poll, 5min)
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: View Event Metrics (Scoped to Tenant)
Admin -[#red]-> Docker: GDPR Data Subject Request
Docker -> DB: gdpr-tools: PII Scan → Cascade Delete\n→ Compliance Receipt
Docker -> Audit: Log GDPR Deletion (compliance receipt)
@enduml
